Source: tano
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Tadej Novak <tadej@tano.si>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), cmake (>=2.6), libqt4-dev (>=4.8.0), libvlc-qt-dev (>=0.8), libx11-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://projects.tano.si

Package: tano
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libtanocore0 (= ${binary:Version}), libtanowidgets0 (= ${binary:Version}), tano-data (= ${source:Version})
Replaces: tano-daemon, tano-recorder, tano-editor
Description: Tano - an open-source cross-platform IP TV player
 Tano is an open-source cross-platform IP TV player. It features
 full IP TV playback with EPG and recorder. Project started
 because of a need of a simple IP TV player on Linux providing EPG.

Package: libtanocore0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libqtcore4 (>=4.8.0), libqtgui4 (>=4.8.0), libqt4-xml (>=4.8.0), libqt4-network (>=4.8.0)
Description: Tano - an open-source cross-platform IP TV player
 Tano is an open-source cross-platform IP TV player. It features
 full IP TV playback with EPG and recorder. Project started
 because of a need of a simple IP TV player on Linux providing EPG.
 .
 This package contains the Tano core library.

